{"tid":2500271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺，日本菜，其實好悶?","createTime":"2021-04-22T13:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T22:24:14.000Z","uid":284284,"like":13,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8f3b0b21bab4404a5495c9fa1ad213e702fece","tid":2500271,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係嗰十幾款野：<br />\n壽司，刺身，拉麵，炸豬扒，丼飯，天婦羅，咖喱飯，大阪燒，鰻魚飯，章魚丸子，烏冬，蕎麥麵，和牛燒肉，長腳蟹，串燒<br />\n<br />\n基本上已經數哂所有日本菜.....<br />\n<br />\n相比起西餐同中菜嗰種千變萬化，無窮無盡，冇固定形態，無限嘅可能性<br />\n我覺得日本菜喺款式多樣變化方面，其實其實真係太過狹窄。"},{"pid":"80567ccae4c9f3b9560e931d26906371baa78f3f","tid":2500271,"uid":129658,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"你窮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真正靚日本菜點止呢d<br />\n剩係玩海鮮都玩到出神入化啦架仔"},{"pid":"0a063acbf06a3b2e3b6e6b25a94d7e150839907a","tid":2500271,"uid":1914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"真，住得日本耐先會覺"},{"pid":"f2523ccf19c80b7ce9df5d96a277c72acf4e760d","tid":2500271,"uid":140125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"80567ccae4c9f3b9560e931d26906371baa78f3f","tid":2500271,"uid":129658,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"你窮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真正靚日本菜點止呢d<br />\n剩係玩海鮮都玩到出神入化啦架仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬又衝出黎7  碌下IG大把新式日本菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae3030f6c694c76c8ae1cccdc62e7683bbf56b6","tid":2500271,"uid":1249,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"其實係，佢哋啲醃料嚟嚟去去都係醬油味醂清酒高湯"},{"pid":"7a7371cc968cfbf2a5a04cb3bacd00ea505296ca","tid":2500271,"uid":1977,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"好食咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c999d11df5eb5e4f59849b0c057e7651c4b363","tid":2500271,"uid":246362,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7e8f3b0b21bab4404a5495c9fa1ad213e702fece","tid":2500271,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係嗰十幾款野：<br />\n壽司，刺身，拉麵，炸豬扒，丼飯，天婦羅，咖喱飯，大阪燒，鰻魚飯，章魚丸子，烏冬，蕎麥麵，和牛燒肉，長腳蟹，串燒<br />\n<br />\n基本上已經數哂所有日本菜.....<br />\n<br />\n相比起西餐同中菜嗰種千變萬化，無窮無盡，冇固定形態，無限嘅可能性<br />\n我覺得日本菜喺款式多樣變化方面，其實其實真係太過狹窄。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"拉麵净係個湯都已經可以有幾十個家系，唔同材料既湯底<br />\n<br />\n仲有壽喜燒 藥膳 懷石料理 蛋包飯 茶泡飯<br />\n隨口up多幾樣都即刻有<br />\n<br />\n而且咖哩飯，意大利粉，中華料理etc既外國料理， 都可以用日本方式煮d hybrid口味出黎<br />\n<br />\n邊度狹窄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a0b77f0ceb7aebb05e5a0279f5ea85ec242c34","tid":2500271,"uid":82398,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"印度淨係食咖喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feba8b81adaebe9fa8376168d95757c311183c53","tid":2500271,"uid":73464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"其實日本都有好多印度餐廳，而且幾正宗"},{"pid":"9ce4a4a601b7340f428d34ee55ed434fa0eaae0e","tid":2500271,"uid":167148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"日本大學食飯都好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d95e6c9358940d1a039945526256f193f4e620","tid":2500271,"uid":182683,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"其實一樣野好唔好食 唔係剩係靠廚師識煮就得<br />\n日本啲勁既廚師係識由零開始種/養啲食材出黎 點都起碼對食材有好強既知識 所以先唔洗咁多花巧野 <br />\n<br />\n你望吓港式茶記個menu百幾樣野 冇野掂 因為全部用啲垃圾材料煮出黎 咩都係攞個啲劣質野 咪要咁多花臣野"},{"pid":"500dfb4b2b10ab429e42db9adf7466f5ed6261d2","tid":2500271,"uid":197201,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:56:56.000Z",